00:13:12,560 --> 00:13:13,760
Kau sungguh berpikir begitu?

230
00:13:13,830 --> 00:13:17,470
Tapi jika suatu saat kau
merasa kehilangan jati dirimu,

231
00:13:17,530 --> 00:13:19,530
