00:29:36,240 --> 00:29:38,240
kau juga meremehkanku!

455
00:29:38,310 --> 00:29:39,510
Itu tak benar!

456
00:29:40,080 --> 00:29:44,220
Kau mempermainkan perasaanku
dan membuatku terlihat bodoh.

457
00:29:44,750 --> 00:29:45,720
Pergilah!

458
00:29:45,780 --> 00:29:46,850
Aku tak akan pergi.

459
00:29:46,920 --> 00:29:48,620
- Pergi sekarang!
- Tidak!

460
00:29:49,190 --> 00:29:51,330
- Pergi saja!
- Aku tak akan pergi!

461
00:29:51,390 --> 00:29:53,090
- Biarkan aku sendiri!
- Tidak!

462
00:29:53,660 --> 00:29:56,500
Hentikan! Tidak!

463
00:29:58,230 --> 00:29:59,500
Lepaskan aku!

464
00:29:59,560 --> 00:30:00,760
Taiga!

465
00:30:00,830 --> 00:30:03,270
- Hentikan!
- Taiga!

466
00:30:22,720 --> 00:30:24,920
- Astaga, itu Kaoru?
- Ya!

467
00:30:24,990 --> 00:30:27,430
- Aku kembali!
- Selamat! Kau tampan sekali!

468
00:30:27,490 --> 00:30:28,460
Dor dor!

469
00:30:35,870 --> 00:30:37,100
Selamat sore.

470
00:30:38,070 --> 00:30:40,340
Bos. Maaf merepotkan.

471
00:30:40,410 --> 00:30:42,010
Tidak apa-apa. Ada apa?

472
00:30:42,640 --> 00:30:44,440
Kau akan kembali menjadi host?

473
00:30:47,250 --> 00:30:50,850
Ya, kupikir aku masih punya
sepuluh sampai lima belas tahun

474
00:30:50,920 --> 00:30:52,820
sebelum aku harus pensiun.

475
00:30:52,880 --> 00:30:56,850
Jadi, aku mau terus lanjut
sampai tak sanggup lagi.

476
